{"tid":310993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馮煒光去北韓狂影女　上fb兼向志願軍致敬","createTime":"2017-07-06T08:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T06:19:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78341eee9b39e8e3c9b349f319e129d71e7d028b","tid":310993,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499318295_26cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499318295_26cf.jpg&h=9d47d7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499314472_6710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499314472_6710.jpg&h=3e810839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499314473_236a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499314473_236a.jpg&h=a7c89cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499314474_1949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499314474_1949.jpg&h=fc4eacb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499314474_cb88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499314474_cb88.jpg&h=b7f64660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499314475_6f4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499314475_6f4a.jpg&h=c63f5500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499314556_f010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499314556_f010.jpg&h=3ccfbbb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c39821616edbf1f834ab78f320b6ad48a223e66","tid":310993,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:52:28.000Z","msg":"卸任新聞統籌專員、轉開公關公司的馮煒光周日在fb發文，表示要出發往北韓，將有4天不能上網，不過，由中國丹東市坐火車去平壤的他之後仍上到fb，更上載在平壤拍到的相片，但很多也是與當地女性合照，包括他稱為平壤「地標」的美女交通警，就連學生也不放過，其友人留言「好多美女相伴」、「帶個女朋友回港」、「左擁右抱」。<br />\n<br />\n馮煒光在fb指，去平壤的話，記得多帶人民幣零錢，「那邊十分歡迎人民幣，但沒零錢找續」，從其多張上載相片可見，他去平壤前先參觀鴨綠江斷橋，從丹東市眺望朝鮮新義州時稱「當年韓戰，志願軍便從這裡過江」，之後在平壤也去了紀念中國人民志願軍於朝鮮戰爭中出手相助的「中朝友誼塔」，愛國的他即留言指要「向志願軍致敬」。<br />\n<br />\n馮煒光又上載一些看雜技表演的相片，與當地「紅領巾」小女孩搭膊頭拍照，亦在fb「曬」多張與當地女士的合照，他強調「朝鮮美少女，不愧是『南男北女』，南朝鮮的男，北朝鮮的女（導遊學漢語，操純正普通話，教我這詞）」。入住羊角島飯店的他指晚上去酒店外影街景時「兩個年輕朝鮮美女導遊」會陪著他。另外，他亦拍了一些平壤街景、火車站、地鐵站情況，讚當地「車水馬龍，有的士等客，奔馳也拍到兩部」。<br />\n<br />\n日前在馮煒光fb留言叮囑「唔好搣傳單」的專欄作家屈穎妍亦有再留言，讚平壤的地鐵「好靚，像莫斯科」。民主黨的羅健熙也有留言指「平壤上美帝facebook，小心小心」，有人問其實是否不可拍照，馮煒光在fb回覆稱可以，只要不拍軍人便可，醫生李家仁就叫他「一切小心」。<br />\n<br />\n上月獲北韓釋放回國的22歲瓦姆比爾是維珍尼亞州大學三年級生，2015年12月29日以遊客身份入境北韓，他被指在平壤羊⻆島國際酒店的職員區摘掉政治標語宣傳品，離開北韓時被捕，他認罪並為此公開道歉。去年3月他遭北韓最高法院以顛覆國家罪，判15年勞改。"},{"pid":"354e17bf0ac5fcd4fd9d4ec9b990b9a92ca7be9d","tid":310993,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解佢有特權影"},{"pid":"315c3d27cacc17b0c398d10e700a920fc49a2fc6","tid":310993,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有特權</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c1fd4a747ac0665fdc8de40ee05c593b8cdfcbe7","tid":310993,"uid":24730,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:56:30.000Z","msg":"怪叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d863105c094ed661c6d4890414804ffbeaeaa52","tid":310993,"uid":15815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:57:17.000Z","msg":"入民主黨後投共<br />\n呢條career path 唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7b0a980096ee2fc25e8b1d1eb258054df7386e","tid":310993,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"金仔捉佢座返十日八日先啦"},{"pid":"c1fa14209706b6852d50b17bc4e54bf9414a07eb","tid":310993,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:59:02.000Z","msg":"舉報佢"},{"pid":"eddf851a9b1cd44839aeec63a15e31870ac5d24c","tid":310993,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"犬決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e142b56f66bfa0ca14ca21951f73a6af94efca","tid":310993,"uid":115525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n金仔可唔可以真係捉鳩左佢<br />\n<br />\n反正呢條廢柴對支那/香港/美國都冇用架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadeafae7746b15cfb594c0443a4241abf479914","tid":310993,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20131206/large/06lp2p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A